{"tid":2315372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"許智峯全家被凍結資產呢單野好應該煲大佢(2)","createTime":"2020-12-07T06:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T06:58:54.000Z","uid":127929,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bd5b1b8abe6f484616da0ae09339e1f6e401019c","tid":2315372,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:54:51.000Z","msg":"見冇人講我就講：<br />\n<br />\n1. 棄保頂盡只能充公保釋金，不能凍結或充公當事人資產<br />\n2. 許智峯冇汲及任何洗黑錢，仍被非法凍結資產<br />\n3. 佢家人沒有汲及任何案件，亦被非法凍結資產<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">呢單野唔係個別例子，港共今日可以咁樣對待一個香港人，他人同樣地可以咁樣對待任何外國人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">TLDR：<br />\n</span></span><br />\n只要睇唔順眼任何係香港既外資 &gt; 港共即可隨意凍結其在港資產 &gt; 外國資金放係香港隨時渣都冇 &gt; 仲夠擔投資係香港呢個黑洞？"},{"pid":"65d3fdf9b076c1a8beab2b95aeeff660695990ec","tid":2315372,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:55:33.000Z","msg":"冇人推你咪推囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2ed9abd28249776a2af942127dedbec28e52ab","tid":2315372,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6676cbbdc268fbd64206ca66955bd85cc3d9d145","tid":2315372,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:55:53.000Z","msg":"汁：<br />\n<br />\n【最新】消息：相關銀行今早再收警方通知凍結許智峯及其家人戶口<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<a href=\"https://news.now.com/urgentnews.jsp?taskId=19702&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Furgentnews.jsp%3FtaskId%3D19702%26refer%3DShare&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYThVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=978f9735\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%